OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774365082
OL,3,C'Star witness' who helped unpick
OL,4,Cmurderer's conspiracy
OL,6,FA woman who has described herself as
OL,7,Fthe one time best friend of convicted
OL,8,Fkiller Stephen McCullagh has said he
OL,9,Fis a "very manipulative, very cold and
OL,10,Fcalculated person."
OL,12,FAnne McCullough gave evidence during
OL,13,Fthe trial of Stephen McCullagh, and
OL,14,Fwas described in court as a "star
OL,15,Fwitness".
OL,17,FAnne has spoken about her friendship
OL,18,Fwith McCullagh in her only interview
OL,19,Fabout the case.
OL,26,@qD@FOUrD@SO]vD@]OUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774365082
OL,3,C'Star witness' who helped unpick
OL,4,Cmurderer's conspiracy
OL,6,FMcCullagh phoned Anne from a police
OL,7,Fcar outside Natalie McNally's home in
OL,8,FLurgan moments after he found her body.
OL,10,F"He phoned me, he was crying, he was
OL,11,Fscreaming, he was howling, 'She's
OL,12,Fgone, she's gone."
OL,14,F"He was so upset and incoherent at
OL,15,Ftimes," Anne told UTV in her only
OL,16,Finterview about her previous
OL,17,Ffriendship with McCullagh.
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@RO]vD@AOUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774365082
OL,3,C'Star witness' who helped unpick
OL,4,Cmurderer's conspiracy
OL,6,F"I couldn't get him to calm down and
OL,7,Fit was actually a police officer that
OL,8,Fhad to take the phone from him and
OL,9,Fexplain what was going on," she said.
OL,11,F"I believe now that it was all an act.
OL,12,FI believe it was all to pull at
OL,13,Fheartstrings."
OL,15,FOn that night, McCullagh had asked
OL,16,FAnne to come with him to Natalie's
OL,17,Fhouse when he had not heard from her.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@[O]sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774365082
OL,3,C'Star witness' who helped unpick
OL,4,Cmurderer's conspiracy
OL,6,FHowever, Anne decided not to go -
OL,7,Fsomething she says she is very
OL,8,Fthankful for given that she would have
OL,9,Fended up finding Natalie's body in her
OL,10,Fhouse.
OL,12,F"It's very distressing. I relive that
OL,13,Fmoment quite a lot and I'm very
OL,14,Fgrateful that I was taught to trust my
OL,15,Fgut.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774365082
OL,3,C'Star witness' who helped unpick
OL,4,Cmurderer's conspiracy
OL,6,F"My gut instinct said don't go and I'm
OL,7,Fvery glad I listened to that because
OL,8,FI'm very fortunate in that I get to
OL,9,Fremember Natalie as I knew her and not
OL,10,Fthe horrible position that she was
OL,11,Fleft in.
OL,13,F"I've suffered from nightmares ever
OL,14,Fsince. I've suffered from flashbacks,"
OL,15,Fshe explained.
OL,17,F"If I see somebody who resembles him
OL,18,Fon the bus, I immediately have a panic
OL,19,Fand sometimes have to just get off the
OL,20,Fbus.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@fO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774365082
OL,3,C'Star witness' who helped unpick
OL,4,Cmurderer's conspiracy
OL,6,F"If I don't hear from somebody in my
OL,7,Ffamily or one of my friends for a
OL,8,Fcouple of hours, I immediately panic
OL,9,Fthat something must be wrong because
OL,10,Fthat's what happened the last time I
OL,11,Fdidn't hear from Natalie.
OL,13,FDays before McCullagh murdered Natalie
OL,14,FMcNally, he lied to Anne about his
OL,15,Fplans to live stream on the night he
OL,16,Fkilled Natalie.
OL,18,F"I still can't wrap my head around any
OL,19,Ffathomable reason why he would lie.
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774365082
OL,3,C'Star witness' who helped unpick
OL,4,Cmurderer's conspiracy
OL,6,F"He created a situation where this
OL,7,Fplayed like an alibi - an astounding
OL,8,Famount of lies to put together in
OL,9,Fadvance.
OL,11,F"Once I saw that he had been re-
OL,12,Farrested and that he had given that
OL,13,Fstatement that the live stream was pre-
OL,14,Frecorded, that cemented in my mind
OL,15,Fthat he has done this.
OL,17,FSpeaking about what McCullagh was
OL,18,Flike, Anne said he could be the
OL,19,F"biggest personality in the room."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU{D@AOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774365082
OL,3,C'Star witness' who helped unpick
OL,4,Cmurderer's conspiracy
OL,6,F"He was boisterous, he was loud, he
OL,7,Fwas jolly, he was so very, very funny
OL,8,Fat times and there were other times he
OL,9,Fsucked up all the air in the room.
OL,11,F"Everything was about him. He was
OL,12,Fangry.
OL,14,F"You know, nothing was more important
OL,15,Fthan what he was going through at that
OL,16,Ftime. so, at times he was difficult to
OL,17,Fbe with.
OL,19,FWhilst testifying against McCullagh,
OL,20,FAnne was able to give evidence
OL,21,Fremotely into the courtroom.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774365082
OL,3,C'Star witness' who helped unpick
OL,4,Cmurderer's conspiracy
OL,6,F"I honestly feel like had I been face
OL,7,Fto face with him in the courtroom, he
OL,8,Fwould have done everything he could to
OL,9,Ftry and intimidate me into not
OL,10,Fanswering," she explained.
OL,12,FSince giving evidence, Anne has faced
OL,13,Fbacklash from people for her one time
OL,14,Ffriendship with McCullagh.
OL,16,F"I have had people, not publicly take
OL,17,Fissue with me, but distance themselves.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774365082
OL,3,C'Star witness' who helped unpick
OL,4,Cmurderer's conspiracy
OL,6,F"There was rumours put around where I
OL,7,Flive that he was my brother and that,
OL,8,Fyou know, he was a member of my family
OL,9,Fand obviously isn't, we're not even
OL,10,Frelated," she said, given the
OL,11,Fsimilarity of their surnames.
OL,13,F"It's caused genuine distress and
OL,14,Fdamage to not just myself but my whole
OL,15,Ffamily.
OL,17,F"He is not my friend. I do not think
OL,18,Fhe is a good person.
OL,20,F"I don't think he was ever the person
OL,21,Fthat he portrayed himself to be.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@IO]uD@AOUyD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774365082
OL,3,C'Star witness' who helped unpick
OL,4,Cmurderer's conspiracy
OL,6,FAnne was reticent about speaking out
OL,7,Fin public, but wanted to in memory of
OL,8,FNatalie who she described as a friend.
OL,10,F"She was wonderful. She was so funny.
OL,11,FShe was just such a wonderfully kind
OL,12,Fperson.
OL,14,F"She would have been a great mum.
OL,16,F"I was making baby hats. I was
OL,17,Fplanning to make baby blankets.
OL,19,F"I was getting wee bits and pieces
OL,20,Fready because they were going to have
OL,21,Fthis child.
OL,26,@rD@AOUvD@AOUxD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
